item.dc:creator: @xerozcheez xerozcheez
item.description:
@xerozcheez wrote:

kenashi:

I like them both, but Family guy copies 95% of everything the simpsons do. It’s easy to prove they do too sadly.

That’s because the simpsons have done nearly everything ;), but family guy definatly don’t have as good stories, but is funnier (although I agree with the South Park episode about Peter always going “oh you mean like that time…” XD), futurama is great though as it’s funny as family guy and has as good stories as the simpsons, but overall I like South Park the best, has decent story line and is by far the funniest, and they rip off a lot of celebs too which us a crease. So imo: South Park > Futurama > Simpsons > Family Guy
